   \"example\": \"Building a tool that uses Claude's brain to extract a clean summary, action items, and decisions from meeting notes.\"\n},\n\n{\n   \"type\": \"insight\",\n   \"difficulty\": 5,\n   \"front\": \"What is the progression of building with Claude?\",\n   \"back\": \"Level 1: Markdown files that Claude reads. Level 2: AI that knows your world and gets smarter over time. Level 3: Agents saved in instructions for repeatable workflows. Level 4: Complex tasks compressed into a single command. Level 5: Tools with AI built-in and tailored exactly to how you work.\",\n   \"insight\": \"The ability to think clearly about what you want and communicate it effectively is the skill being built with Claude.\",\n   \"mistake\": \"Not understanding the progression of building with Claude.\",\n   \"example\": \"Building a tool that uses Claude's brain to extract a clean summary, action items, and decisions from meeting notes.\"\n}\n]"
