  "chunk_length": 5454,
  "target_count": 4,
  "raw_text": "[\n{\n  \"type\": \"concept\",\n   \"difficulty\": 3,\n   \"front\": \"What is the power of local context in Claudesys?\",\n   \"back\": \"The power of local context in Claudesys is its ability to compound. This means that every future conversation in this folder will have access to the updated context on who you are.\",\n   \"insight\": \"Local context allows Claudesys to learn and improve over time.\",\n   \"mistake\": \"Assuming Claudesys has no memory or context.\",\n   \"example\": \"When you create a file, Claudesys updates its context and can access it in future conversations.\"\n},\n\n{\n   \"type\": \"mcq\",\n   \"difficulty\": 4,\n   \"front\": \"What is an agent in Claudesys?\",\n   \"back\": \"An agent is a saved set of instructions that tells Claudesys how to do a specific type of task. Instead of re-explaining your preferences every time, you write them down once, and then invoke the agent when needed.\",\n   \"options\": [\n      \"A set of files in a specific folder\",\n      \"A saved set of instructions that tells Claudesys how to do a specific task\",\n      \"A type of file in Claudesys\",\n      \"A way to exit Claudesys\"\n   ],\n   \"correctAnswer\": \"A saved set of instructions that tells Claudesys how to do a specific task\",\n   \"insight\": \"Agents help Claudesys learn and improve over time.\",\n   \"mistake\": \"Assuming agents are just files in a folder.\",\n   \"example\": \"Think of an agent like a recipe: you write it down once, and then follow it every time you need to make something.\"\n},\n\n{\n   \"type\": \"problem\",\n   \"difficulty\": 5,\n   \"front\": \"Create a simple agent that helps you write a quick end-of-day reflection.\",\n   \"back\": \"To create an agent, tell Claudesys something like: 'I want to build a journaling agent. Every evening, I should be able to type /journal and it should ask me what I accomplished today, what I want to carry into tomorrow, and what's on my mind. Then it saves my answers as a clean journal entry with today's date.'\",\n   \"insight\": \"Agents can help you automate repetitive tasks and improve your productivity.\",\n   \"mistake\": \"Assuming agents are too complex to create.\",\n   \"example\": \"Let's build a simple 'daily journal' agent that helps you write a quick end-of-day reflection.\"\n},\n\n{\n   \"type\": \"insight\",\n   \"difficulty\": 4,\n   \"front\": \"Why are agents an important feature in Claudesys?\",\n   \"back\": \"Agents are an important feature in Claudesys because they allow you to automate repetitive tasks and improve your productivity. By creating agents, you can save time and energy, and focus on more important things.\",\n   \"insight\": \"Agents help Claudesys learn and improve over time.\",\n   \"mistake\": \"Assuming agents are just a novelty feature.\",\n   \"example\": \"Think of agents as a way to level up your productivity and efficiency in Claudesys.\"\n}\n]"
